Description
As a PO I want the login functionality to be developed and integrated into Banking application

Acceptance Criteria

Page title

Labels for username, password and error message.\

Text-boxes for username and password

Username and password validation:

If both fields are empty : Username  and password are required

If username field is empty: Please enter username

If password field is empty: Please enter password

If login info is incorrect: Invalid credentials

Username field should allow any text to be entered as username

Redirect to Account Summary only when Valid username and valid password are entered

5. Login button that redirects to Account Summary page (after validation)